
= a editorial and crowdsourced data journalism platform that maps who's who in business and politics in Chile

URL = http://poderopedia.org


=Description=

"Poderopedia is a editorial and crowdsourced data journalism platform that maps who's who in business and politics in Chile. Using data visualization and semantic technology, Poderopedia helps you understand the connections between the most influential people, businesses and organizations to reflect any conflicts of interest and promote transparency so information and power are available to everyone.
Poderopedia is a nonprofit open source project by Poderomedia Foundation, with awesome support from Knight Foundation and Start-Up Chile."


=More Information= 

To learn more please go to poderopedia.org


